channel.title: Were Do I Change A DeathSpawn?
channel.description:
The server base I am using is Deltascape.
The only thing I need is to move teleports when you die
I want them to change to edgeville, but on delta its like when u telehome or die its like a random spot of that part of falador.
So can someone help me change it to a random spot of edgeville?
Thanks, Jamie14

item.title: Were Do I Change A DeathSpawn?
item.dc:creator: @sanity sanity
item.description:
@sanity wrote:

Very easy, search coordinates you get when you die (the respawn point) search for them in the client.java and then change to the new coords you want at death.

::mypos - command for coords

Read full topic
